  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6750427/" class="title-link">书名为什么没有翻译成“半边天”？作者名为什么...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6750427"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yimei/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1044294-50.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yimei/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">一湄</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-07-21"
      class="main-meta">2014-07-21 19:47:42</span>
</div>

