  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6669928/" class="title-link">读《天空的另一半》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6669928"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2568257/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2568257-12.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2568257/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">星期天先森</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-05-15"
      class="main-meta">2014-05-15 16:08:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6669928_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《天空的另一半》书写下了一系列第三世界女性的恶劣遭遇与不放弃的奋斗挣扎，这些女性之所以遭到奴役与暴力，有其十分复杂的文化、权力结构与政治经济因素。例如基于性别偏好而堕掉女胎、全球化运作的性贩运、阴蒂切除、荣誉谋杀、荣誉强暴，或者，将羞辱家庭的荣誉强暴扩展到...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6669928/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">23有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
